In the meantime, if you use `FluxMixin` in your route handlers, then you can make sure they get your flux instance as a prop by [using `createElement`](https://github.com/rackt/react-router/blob/master/docs/API.md#createelementcomponent-props):

``` javascript
var flux = new Fluxxor.Flux(...);

// make sure react router injects the `flux` prop
// into every component it instantiates
function createFluxComponent(Component, props) {
  return <Component {...props} flux={flux} />;
}

var router = (
  <Router history={history} createElement={createFluxComponent}>
```

